As Neneko approaches the leader of the Lilis,\. Zokuki sits up with clear interest.\.\.
She was lounging on top of what looked like the inside of a helmet like it was a throne.\.\. Neneko had no doubts she probably stole that from one of the dwarves up top.\.\.
Admittedly considering how tiny everyone here was,\. their penchant for banditry was pretty impressive.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Well well!\.\. What's this,\. what's this!?\.\. You're not one of mine!\.\. Not one of the great Zokuki's!
\n<\n[1]>That's right!\.\. I'm Neneko!\.\. Primest Cat in this Hole!\.\.
Zokuki hops off of the helmet.\.\. Even given Neneko's shrunken size,\. the Lili has to crane her neck to look up at her face.\.\.
She steps forward and begins peering at the catgirl,\. her big black eyes giving Neneko a curious once over.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>You're no Lili...\.\.\. you look like a Beast,\. but you're like one of us,\. too!\.\. That's freaky,\. freaky!
\n<\n[1]>Hahh...\.\.\. guess I'm just special like that,\. eh?\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Hmm...\.\.\. you're not as cute as my boys...\.\.\. \BST[1]but!~\.\. But!~
Zokuki huffs,\. then gives a nod,\. crossing her arms.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>You can be of use to Zokuki anyway,\. yes!\.\. Yes!~\.\. Be grateful,\. Neneneneko!\.\. If you pledge loyalty to me,\. then you can be one of mine too!\.\. Mwahahaha!
\n<\n[1]>You've definitely got a reeeeeeal impressive place here,\. Zokuki.\.\. I mean,\. just look at how organized everything is!\.\.
\n<\v[462]>I do!\.\. I do!\.\. It's good that you've noticed my amazingness!
\n<\n[1]>Oh yeah,\. you're amazingness is tooootally...\.\.\. amazing.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>I'm just,\. like,\. in awe and stuff.\.\. You're really living in luxury.\.\. And all these Lilis,\. it's real obvious how much they admire you.\.\. How do you do it?\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Mwahahaha!\.\. If you're hoping to copy me and gain some good boys of you're own,\. then you're out of luck,\. Neneneneneko!
\n<\v[462]>My brilliance is my own!\.\. And so is my charisma!~\.\. No Lili or even a weird Lili-\.like Beasty can be like me!~
Zokuki laughs proudly.\.\. Neneko looks on in exasperation.\.\.
Something tells her this girl is REALLY easy to work with.\.\. Just gotta lay on the compliments.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>I guess every brilliant and amazing leader's gotta have their secrets,\. huh?\.\.
Zokuki laughs again.\.\. Such impressive arrogance.\.\. Neneko had a lot of pride herself but this little shorty was on a whole other level.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>So that must mean you know aaaaall about the Fortress up top right?\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Ohoh!\.\. Yes!\.\. They are good targets!~\.\. \BST[3]That fat black haired Dwarfy Dwarf calls herself the Queen of this Fortress,\. but we all know that I am the true Queen!~
\n<\n[1]>Hahhh.\.\. So as Queen you must know a lot of things the Dwarves don't,\. eh?\.\.
\n<\v[462]>What do you take me for?\.\. A fake!?\.\. Of course,\. of course!\.\. My boys are in every wall!~\.\. We seeeeee everything!
\n<\v[462]>Like all the guards sneaking off to get lewd and naked when the Queen isn't looking!
\n<\n[1]>Er...\.\.\. and anything else?\.\. \BST[5]Anything shady?\.\. Suspicious?\.\. Secret-\.y?\.\.
Zokuki blinks,\. tilting her head.\.\. She puts a hand to her chin.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Hmmm...\.\.\. we've seen a lotta things in this Fortress...\.\.\. I can't really think of specific things...
\n<\n[1]>Yeah,\. like,\. someone being taken somewhere,\. without their consent.\.\. You know,\. as an example.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>...\.\.\. \BST[5]Oh!\.\. Yes!\.\. Neneko's smarter than she looks!
\n<\v[462]>That's right,\. that's right!\.\. I've seen that!\.\. A few times!
\n<\v[462]>Uh huh,\. uh huh!\.\. I don't think even the fake Dwarf Queen knows about it!
Zokuki turns around,\. walking back to the helmet and hopping back onto it,\. sitting down.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>At nighty night time,\. when the Fortress sleeps,\. we're still awake,\. plotting and sneaking~
\n<\v[462]>There,\. when none of the dwarves are watching,\. people that don't look like dwarves go through the Fortress,\. into that place they call the Caldera Shrine.
\n<\v[462]>And those people carry other people!\.\. And then...
Neneko stumbles back,\. feeling as if she's been gut punched.\.\. She wasn't expecting an actual lead...!!\.\.
\n<\v[462]>My boys are always listening in~\.\. Apparently there's a Lift in there~\.\. But we've never seen one of those people that show up at night use it to come back up!\.\. A one way trip!
At this,\. Zokuki tilts her head,\. looking thoughtful.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>But from what the dumb smelly dwarves have said,\. only the fake Queen can turn the Lift on,\. but she's always asleep when those mystery people come and use it.
\n<\n[1]>Only the Queen can use the Lift?\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Kekeke...\.\.\. are you curious?~\.\. Well,\. here's the special thing!~\.\. Something you're only hearing cuz you're one of mine,\. Neneneneneko!~
The Lili Bandit leans forward,\. a mischievous grin on her face.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>That fake Queen has \c[18]a very special treasure\c[0]...
\n<\v[462]>So you know about it!!~\.\. Yes yes,\. you have a good eye!\.\. Good!
\n<\v[462]>That's right...\.\.\. that big,\. green shiny.\.\. The \ii[23].\.\. It's magic,\. you know?\.\. Magic!
\n<\v[462]>That dumb dumb dwarf queen always keeps it close by.\.\. And whenever she needs to turn on the Lift she uses it to power it,\. mmhm.
\n<\v[462]>I dunno how the mystery people use the Lift without it,\. but I don't care!\.\. Cuz,\. cuz!
\n<\v[462]>The \ii[23]!~\.\. I want it!~\.\. If that fake Queen parades it around all day then I want it!\.\. It will prove that I am the true Queen of this Fortress!~
\n<\v[462]>I'll use its magic much much better than her!\.\. All she ever does is hold and stare at it!~\.\. The Arkengem belongs to the Lilis!\.\. \BST[1]Because I say so!~\.\. Mwahahaha~!
Neneko crosses her arms,\. ignoring Zokuki's ramblings.\.\.

If what the Lili said was true,\. then it means the chances her brother is still on this Stratum are next to none...\.\.\. which means she needs to use that Lift to keep chasing those kidnappers down.\.\.
And if she needs to use the Lift...\.\.\.
Neneko clicks her tongue,\. but ignores that comment.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Surely,\. if you want the gem so much,\. you must already have a plan in the works,\. right?\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Hm hm hm~\.\. Yes,\. as a matter of fact,\. I do!~\.\. \BST[5]A good plan!\.\. A perfect plan!~
\n<\n[1]>Well,\. I am your...\.\.\. servant,\. right?\.\. \BST[1,Neneko2]And I wanna help steal that gem!\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Oh yeah!\.\. I mean...\.\.\. I can't really "serve" you the way your...\.\.\. boys do.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>So what better way to prove myself useful to the boss around here than to show off my skills?\.\.~
\n<\n[1]>I'm a master at sneaking and ruining people's day,\. ya know?\.\.~
Zokuki hrrrrrms loudly,\. eying Neneko over again.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Yes,\. yes...\.\.\. I can see it!\.\. Very well!\.\. Neneneneko!\.\. You shall prove yourself to the Lili Bandits by stealing the \ii[23] for me!
\n<\v[462]>Do so and you will be rewarded!\.\. Loved!\.\. Treated as kin!\.\. Truly as one of mine!~\.\. \BST[5]You may not ever be one of my boys but you will be my number one girl!\.\. Number one!
\n<\n[1]>That mean I get to use the \ii[23]?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Err,\. well,\. I mean.\.\. Has any of your bandits ever seen what's on the other side of the Lift?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Don't ya wanna know what's down there?\.\. There might be even more treasures...\.\.\. \BST[2]I'm a real curious cat,\. so...\.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>I see...\.\.\. I see...\.\.\. you wish to scout for more Lili territory and treasure!\.\. \BST[1]You've got an eye for the future!
\n<\v[462]>Yes!\.\. Yes!\.\. If you can get the \ii[23],\. we can use it on the Lift and send you down!~
\n<\v[462]>Ahahahaha!~\.\. Alright then!\.\. Now,\. here's the plan!
Zokuki leans in,\. lowering her voice to a conspiratory whisper.\.\. Neneko's ear twitches as she listens in.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>The Queen never lets the gem out of her sight.\.\. \BST[1]Not even during bath time.
\n<\v[462]>It'll be impossible to steal it when she's working or relaxing,\. no no...\.\.\. \BST[5]But!~
\n<\v[462]>Lately,\. something interesting has been happening in the Queen's room at night...\.\.\. yes yes.\.\. At around 5,\. every night...
\n<\v[462]>The Queen's personal guard has been accompanying her to her room,\. just the two of them,\. even sending the door guards away.
\n<\v[462]>Yes yes...\.\.\. fat,\. dumb,\. blondie,\. looks real serious and boring.
Neneko thinks about who that could be...\.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Mmhm,\. mmhm.\.\. She makes all the guards leave and says a buncha stuff about the Queen needing peace and quiet and then they both stay in the room for a long time~
\n<\n[1]>Wow...\.\.\. spicy,\. didn't think queenie had it in her...\.\.\. or had that kinda taste...\.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>It's the one time where the fake Queen is most distracted!\.\. AND the one time with the least amount of guards!~
\n<\v[462]>It's the perfect time to sneak in,\. grab the \ii[23],\. and leave!~
Zokuki cackles at the brilliance of her plan.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Once the Queen notices her precious gem is gone,\. she'll go on a rampage!~
\n<\v[462]>The dwarves will tear themselves apart!~\.\. \BST[1]They'll blame everyone and everything and even each other!~
\n<\v[462]>They'll never expect that the gem is still inside the Fortress,\. hidden away in my hoard!~
\n<\v[462]>And once they've all destroyed each other,\. I'll claim this big Fortress and all of its food as the true Queen!\.\. Bahahahaha!~
\n<\n[1]>Eesh...\.\.\. you really dream big,\. huh shortie?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Sorry,\. sorry...\.\.\. \BST[5,Neneko]right,\. well,\. I don't really care about the whole throwing the Stratum into anarchy thing,\. but I've got the gist of my part of the plan.\.\.
\n<\v[462]>Good!\.\. Be quick about it and we will throw a feast...\.\.\. \BST[1]in my honor,\. of course!~
Neneko shakes her head.\.\. Looks like it's time to pull off a "big" heist.\.\.
